Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: medialog.imageexport
Version: 0.5
Summary: Export Plone images pil scale imagescale
Home-page: http://www.medialog.no
Author: Espen Moe-Nilssen
Author-email: espen@medialog.no
License: GPL
Description: Introduction
        ============
        
        Adds a browser view to export all images from a folder as a zip file.
        
        Currently, scales settings is not working for Dexterity Images (the original size is exported)
        
        
        Use it like this: http://mysite/myfolder/image-export
        
        
        
        
        And with archetype
        ------------------
        http://mysite/myfolder/image-export?imagesize=mini
        
        http://mysite/myfolder/image-export?imagesize=thumb
        
        
        Changelog
        =========
        
        0.5 (2016-04-04)
        ----------------
        * Plone 5 support
        * Image scales does not work with Dexterity (News and Images etc). The Original scale is exported
        
        
        0.4.2 (2014-11-28)
        ----------------
        * Fixed Unicode error if image names had some strange characters in them.
        
        
        0.4.1 (2014-11-27)
        ----------------
        * New release since some files was not included (added Manifest to solve it)
        
        
        0.4 (2014-02-09)
        ----------------
            
        * added browser view to choose image size to export 
        * added (folder) action
        
        
        0.3 (2012-09-20)
        ----------------
            
        * added the browser view to "collection"
        * added support for dexterity content types
        
        
        0.2 (2012-12-05)
        ----------------
            
        * downloaded images now gets the right suffix.
        
        
        0.1 (2011-05-12)
        ----------------
            
        * first version
